        </item>
        <item>
            <title>多色圓角效能升級 Samsung Galaxy S25 系列外觀規格全面流出</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/13/samsung-galaxy-s25-series-render-leak/genai-and-cloud/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=samsung-galaxy-s25-series-render-leak</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/13/samsung-galaxy-s25-series-render-leak/genai-and-cloud/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[arthur]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2025 02:00:42 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[GenAI 與雲端科技專區]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[google]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[metaeye]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Uncategorized]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[VR 科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Windows 11]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[區塊鏈]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手提電話]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[智慧城市]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Galaxy S25]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[samsung]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1286566</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">距離三星 Galaxy Unpacked 發佈會越來越近，有關 Galaxy S25 系列新機的消息亦越來越多。近日，外媒 Android Headlines 獨家曝光了多張 Galaxy S25 系列官方渲染圖，完整揭露了 S25、S25+和 S25 Ultra 三款新機的外觀設計及配色。與此同時，更詳細的規格信息亦被披露</span><span style="font-weight: 400;"><br /></span><span style="font-weight: 400;">。</span></p><h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">設計革新</span></h2><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">相比上一代產品，新系列最顯著的設計變化出現在 Galaxy S25 Ultra 上，其邊角設計變得更為圓潤。三款機型均採用平面屏幕、平面機背及直邊框設計，邊框在邊緣處略有弧度。值得注意的是，相機模組設計也有所改良，採用上寬下窄的設計，靈感源自傳統相機鏡頭桶的外觀。</span></p><h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">多彩配色方案</span></h2><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">三星為不同機型提供了獨特的配色選擇：</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Galaxy S25 及 S25+提供冰藍色、薄荷綠、海軍藍和銀影色四種選擇</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1286571" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/samsunggalaxys25plus-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/samsunggalaxys25plus-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/samsunggalaxys25plus.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/samsunggalaxys25plus-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Galaxy S25 Ultra 則主打高端質感，推出鈦黑色、鈦灰色、鈦銀藍色及鈦白銀色四款配色</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1286572" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/samsunggalaxys25ultr-3-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/samsunggalaxys25ultr-3-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/samsunggalaxys25ultr-3.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/samsunggalaxys25ultr-3-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1286569" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/samsunggalaxys25ultr-2-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/samsunggalaxys25ultr-2-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/samsunggalaxys25ultr-2.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/samsunggalaxys25ultr-2-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1286567" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/samsunggalaxys25ultr-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/samsunggalaxys25ultr-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/samsunggalaxys25ultr.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/samsunggalaxys25ultr-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1286568" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/samsunggalaxys25ultr-1-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/samsunggalaxys25ultr-1-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/samsunggalaxys25ultr-1.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/samsunggalaxys25ultr-1-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><h2><span style="font-weight: 400;">硬件規格升級</span></h2><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">根據已曝光的規格信息，S25 系列三款新機均搭載高通驍龍 8 Elite for Galaxy 處理器，預計是驍龍 8 Elite 的超頻版本，性能表現值得期待。此外，三款新機均配備 12GB RAM，而 S25 Ultra 在部分市場更可能提供 16GB RAM 版本。系統方面，S25 系列將預載基於 Android 15 的 One UI 7 客製化介面，並支持 Wi-Fi 7 和藍牙 5.3 等最新無線技術。</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Galaxy S25 Ultra 規格：</span></p><ul><li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">6.9 吋 WQHD+ Dynamic AMOLED 2X 屏幕</span></li><li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">120Hz 自適應刷新率</span></li><li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">5000mAh 大容量電池，支援 45W 快充</span></li><li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">後置四鏡頭系統：200MP 主攝 + 50MP 超廣角 + 10MP 長焦 (3 倍光學變焦) + 50MP 潛望式長焦 (5 倍光學變焦)</span></li></ul><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Galaxy S25+規格：</span></p><ul><li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">6.7 吋 WQHD+ Dynamic AMOLED 2X 屏幕</span></li><li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">4900mAh 電池，支援 45W 快充</span></li><li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">後置三鏡頭系統，配置與標準版相同</span></li></ul><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Galaxy S25 規格：</span></p><ul><li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">6.2 吋 FHD+ Dynamic AMOLED 2X 屏幕</span></li><li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">4000mAh 電池，支援 25W 快充</span></li><li style="font-weight: 400;" aria-level="1"><span style="font-weight: 400;">後置 50MP 主攝 + 12MP 超廣角 + 10MP 長焦三鏡頭系統</span></li></ul><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">三星預計在 1 月 22 日的 Galaxy Unpacked 發佈會上正式發佈新機系列。除了展示硬件規格外，市場預期三星還將重點介紹新一代 AI 智能功能。有傳聞指出可能會同場預告 Galaxy S25 Slim 版本，但細節仍未確定。</span></p><p>來源：<a href="https://www.androidheadlines.com/samsung-galaxy-s25-series-design" target="_blank" rel="noopener">androidheadlines</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
